#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kubrick; is a game based on the <trademark>Rubik's Cube</trademark> puzzle. "
"The cube sizes range from 2x2x2 up to 6x6x6, or you can play with irregular "
"<quote>bricks</quote> such as 5x3x2 or <quote>mats</quote> such as 6x4x1 or "
"2x2x1. The game has a selection of puzzles at several levels of difficulty, "
"as well as demos of pretty patterns and solution moves, or you can make up "
"your own puzzles ..."
msgstr ""
"El &kubrick; és un joc basat en el trencaclosques del <trademark>Cub de "
"Rubik</trademark>. L'interval de mides del cub és des de 2x2x2 a 6x6x6, o es "
"pot jugar amb «maons» irregulars com 5x3x2 o «matrius» com 6x4x1 o 2x2x1. El "
"joc té una selecció de trencaclosques amb diversos nivells de dificultat, "
"així com demostracions de patrons interessants i moviments de solució, o es "
"poden construir trencaclosques propis..."

